## PRO TIPS & SHORTCUTS

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  AFTER EFFECTS SHORTCUTS (SAVE TIME)                │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                      │
│  🎯 KEYFRAMES:                                       │
│  • Alt+[ – Trim start to current time              │
│  • Alt+] – Trim end to current time                │
│  • F9 – Easy ease (smooth animation)               │
│  • Ctrl+Alt+K – Keyframe assistant                 │
│                                                      │
│  🔍 PREVIEW:                                         │
│  • 0 (numpad) – RAM preview                        │
│  • Shift+0 – Preview from here                      │
│  • Ctrl+Shift+X – Cache preview                     │
│                                                      │
│  📝 LAYERS:                                          │
│  • Ctrl+Shift+C – Pre-compose                       │
│  • Ctrl+Alt+Y – New adjustment layer                │
│  • Ctrl+Y – New solid                               │
│  • Ctrl+D – Duplicate layer                         │
│                                                      │
│  🔥 PRO TIP: Use expressions for complex animations │
│  • Hold Alt + click stopwatch – add expression     │
│  • loopOut() – infinite animation                  │
│  • wiggle(5,30) – random movement                  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

